                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8369" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1289</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1944 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鞍本重组，脱胎换骨——钢铁“巨擎”创卓越之治</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ansteel Restructuring Benxi Steel,be born again --Acceleration of cooperation between central and local governments</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">侯志才，王甜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鞍钢集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重组整合；国企改革；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Reorganization and integration;Reform of state-owned enterprises;Cooperation between central and local governments</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国社会主义市场经济的深度发展，新形势不断变化对国有资本的经营现状产生更高要求。改革，作为推动宏观经济与企业发展的首要推动力，尤其在国家战略支柱性钢铁行业，中央与地方国企兼顾企业效益目标与国家发展责任。本案例选取了国企改革三年行动攻坚期，国资委指导下的鞍钢合并整合本钢的企业事件全过程，通过描述从重组前的产业困境到全方位整合融合的顶层设计与流程，尤其是鞍钢重组本钢后，重点描述鞍钢领导下的整合融合工作中，针对本钢企业治理优化目标而执行的多项综合性举措，最终体现出重组各项绩效指标的全面增长。借助案例教学，促使学生理解认识当前我国国企改革的攻坚任务，并从国有企业公司治理方面掌握治理优化与协同效应发挥之间的内在机制。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the deep development of China&#39;s socialist market economy and the continuous changes in the new situation, higher requirements have been placed on the management status of state-owned capital. Reform, as the primary driving force for promoting macroeconomic and enterprise development, especially in the national strategic pillar steel industry, central and local state-owned enterprises balance enterprise efficiency goals and national development responsibilities. This case selects the entire process of Ansteel&#39;s merger and integration of Benxi Steel under the guidance of the State owned Assets Supervision and Administration Commission during the three-year action period of state-owned enterprise reform. By describing the top-level design and process from the industrial difficulties before the restructuring to comprehensive integration and integration, especially the six comprehensive reform measures adopted by Ansteel during the restructuring of Benxi Steel, the new Ansteel&#39;s corporate image was successfully demonstrated, This introduces a new comprehensive reform model that maximizes the synergistic effect of cooperative mergers and acquisitions between central and local state-owned enterprises. Through case studies, the teaching goal of enabling students to understand the methods and methods of state-owned enterprise reform and master the key points of enterprise restructuring and integration is achieved.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与重组》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场势力理论；央企战略重组；产权理论；资源依赖理论；现代企业制度；委托代理理论；规模经济理论；协同价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
